originalText.text: Great location! Communication is great and prenatal massage was one of the best things I’ve experienced. I’ve been dealing with some sciatica pain and after massage with Lisa, it’s gone and I feel brand new. Will definitely be coming back!

originalText.text: Wasn't sure was to expect of a prenatal massage at 32 weeks, but Anne is fantastic and I loved my massage. I leave feeling relaxed and the office is clean, comfortable and soothing. Happy to have found a convenient location on the UES!

originalText.text: I’ve heard of this place many times and so glad they have opened another location on UES. Room is clean and comfy, Anne is truly amazing and works her magic every time. My last trimester has not been easy, I’ve been dragging myself to here every week and walking out feeling amazing and knowing that I will have a much needed good night’s sleep.
